                        { "variable": "q_infl",     "time": 0.0, "expected": 1.3306330914621305e-04 }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "id": "snow_present_skip_evap",
                    "description": "Snow layers present (has_snow=1): Eq. 5.57 branch of the q_infl ifelse selects q_infl = q_liq_0 - q_over (the surface-evaporation term q_seva is NOT subtracted — the snow layer mediates surface evaporation upstream of this component). With q_liq_0=5e-4 and q_seva=1e-4 (active but ignored), q_infl = 5e-4 - q_over = 3.79e-4, identical to the no-evap case at the same q_liq_0. This is the contrast with `evap_exceeds_throughfall` below.",
