                    "id": "evap_exceeds_throughfall",
                    "description": "No snow but evaporation exceeds throughfall (q_seva=2e-4 > q_liq_0-q_over): the max(..., zero_kgpm2s) floor in Eq. 5.56 clamps q_infl to exactly 0 — the surface cannot infiltrate water that has already evaporated. Specifically q_liq_0 - q_over - q_seva = 1e-4 - 2.43e-5 - 2e-4 = -1.24e-4 < 0 ⇒ max(...,0) = 0. Contrasts with snow_present_skip_evap above to isolate the q_seva branch.",
